{"poem":{"text":"A winter evening\nin a basement in Chinatown\nthree women wearing orange scarves\nlecturing about someone who never came back\n\nA spring midnight\nbetween two subway stops\ntwo girls with red hair\nthinking of someone who never closed the door\n\nAn autumn evening\ninside a narrow bookstore\nthree boys all suited up\nwriting about someone who never lost the map\n\nA summer midday\non a platform that smells like rain\nthree girls with pink hair\nrecording sounds about someone who never found the way home","lines":["A winter evening","in a basement in Chinatown","three women wearing orange scarves","lecturing about someone who never came back","","A spring midnight","between two subway stops","two girls with red hair","thinking of someone who never closed the door","","An autumn evening","inside a narrow bookstore","three boys all suited up","writing about someone who never lost the map","","A summer midday","on a platform that smells like rain","three girls with pink hair","recording sounds about someone who never found the way home"]},"createdAt":{"$$date":1772419883788},"_id":"0Y5E8o6GPxvr1itu"}
{"poem":{"text":"A spring morning\non the last ferry to Staten Island\nfour people wearing pink furry coats\nlaughing about someone who never wrote back\n\nA winter midnight\nbetween two subway stops\ntwo boys carrying luggage\ncomplaining about someone who never looked up\n\nA summer morning\non Jay Street\nfour girls with green hair\nthinking of someone who never cried\n\nAn autumn afternoon\nstanding at a crowded bus stop\ntwo men all suited up\nlecturing about someone who never knew what happened","lines":["A spring morning","on the last ferry to Staten Island","four people wearing pink furry coats","laughing about someone who never wrote back","","A winter midnight","between two subway stops","two boys carrying luggage","complaining about someone who never looked up","","A summer morning","on Jay Street","four girls with green hair","thinking of someone who never cried","","An autumn afternoon","standing at a crowded bus stop","two men all suited up","lecturing about someone who never knew what happened"]},"createdAt":{"$$date":1772419890130},"_id":"gp29z9RJ7yMYyRJK"}
